messages.messageBody:
"We all love, love, love The Sims. I am addicted to downloading new "stuff" "


OMG This game is so addicting!! My kids love it too!! I started out single with a small house then worked my way up to a family and a huge house!! Then our p/c crashed along with my hours,days ,months of playing :(.....

I haven't started a new life yet but think about it now and then!! I know how consumed I get and I don't think I have the time now!! LOL Its so much fun buliding your dream house!! and living in it!!




"Do not worry about anything, but in everything by prayer
and supplication with thanksgiving let your requests be
made known to God." Philippians 4.6
